The '''Akashnu Mountains''' stood in the land of [[Malatra]] in [[Kara-Tur]] and were the birthplace of the [[Kuong Kingdom]].<ref group="note">Like many locations in the Kuong Kingdom, the Akashnu Mountains have not been labelled on any map of Malatra, which offer a number of unnamed ranges as candidates.
